{"title":"天气","authors":["叶圣陶"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":6,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"天气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶圣陶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“今天天气哈哈哈”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无语强语资笑哗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧日虚文良可哂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"习焉弗察似无他。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年来时闻谈天气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用心颇与旧日异，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发之由衷形于面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜则轩眉戚凝睇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或谓雨足正应需，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或谓墒歉盼雪腴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或谓催熟炎阳好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或谓扬花风堪虞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"言者未必事农业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非农与农同关切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农为基础入人深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即此端倪堪欣悦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"复忆张市听雨眠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晓看群山浴后鲜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地委书记与客言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜来雨情指掌间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"某县某区量若干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顷已通话遍询焉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"念农无时忘知天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群切知天在制天。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}